{"tid":2304704,"cid":16,"subCid":0,"title":"是靚黃午 自家製豬頸肉漢堡 忌廉芝士汁配炸墨魚肉 黑松露醬配粗著條","createTime":"2020-11-29T04:54:32.000Z","updateTime":"2020-11-29T09:38:08.000Z","uid":33359,"like":236,"dislike":11,"uniUserReply":68,"replies":[{"pid":"94f3586dee59b300e449ea3cbb6e772c5d2389da","tid":2304704,"uid":33359,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-11-29T04:54:32.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/9d7osS9.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2F9d7osS9.jpg&h=f1ca09ef&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/6yTbBMx.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2F6yTbBMx.jpg&h=c6293ad4&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/6LYu7Te.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2F6LYu7Te.jpg&h=32a02a42&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/Kr6HJrB.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FKr6HJrB.jpg&h=2a7d63ef&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n豬頸肉放入漢堡到真係未試過<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/wail.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n今次專登叫黎試吓<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/wail.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n講吓味道先<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/wail.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n豬頸肉極大肉厚<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/wail.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n煎得好香口<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/wail.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n食落口好嫩滑<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/wail.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n成個調味係偏秦式<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/wail.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n加埋個微酸既醬食落又無咁漏<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/wail.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n炸墨魚肉幾香<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/wail.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n可惜D墨魚肉有少少UN<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/wail.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n粗著條雖然係急凍貨<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/wail.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n但佢炸得幾好<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/wail.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n真係外脆內軟個隻<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/wail.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n隻黑松露醬好味過M記個隻煤氣醬多多聲<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/wail.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n食落個百會穴好C伏<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/wail.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"9e7c838e587f95a1a597a181cf1d05345f58a9bc","tid":2304704,"uid":211090,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-11-29T04:54:53.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/wail.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"b2026d3b78919239b3cf18c0d8a6591f19ed294c","tid":2304704,"uid":374180,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-11-29T04:54:56.000Z","msg":"是<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/wail.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"80897b3f5862ce2fe299d3f03e560812a0efd6dc","tid":2304704,"uid":129695,"like":6,"dislike":0,"score":6,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-11-29T04:54:57.000Z","msg":"觀塘<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/wail.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/wail.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"ed7b998e20091772a9d3441804b53d15b4692a7f","tid":2304704,"uid":364608,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-11-29T04:55:01.000Z","msg":"又炸<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/wail.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"1e1382ca01bda6e4af7822aec0e4b669697fe459","tid":2304704,"uid":317378,"like":1,"dislike":8,"score":-7,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-11-29T04:55:02.000Z","msg":"漢堡師<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/wail.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"b0a7e16bdf26a481da8988674dc358919789e300","tid":2304704,"uid":302668,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2020-11-29T04:55:04.000Z","msg":"邊度？<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/wail.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"86e91233faa4cc8905576e4992a672e7be569d36","tid":2304704,"uid":272819,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-11-29T04:55:11.000Z","msg":"美"},{"pid":"fc829ce39f50d5d2b90eca2be790b53135734b1a","tid":2304704,"uid":364806,"like":6,"dislike":1,"score":5,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-11-29T04:55:11.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"57ef40ed066